    "problemStatement": "There is an array AAA with integer elements of size nnn. We create another array BBB where\n\nBiB_{i}Bi\u200b = \u2211j=1iAj\\sum_{j = 1}^{i}A_j\u2211j=1i\u200bAj\u200b - max{A1,A2,....,Ai}max\\{A_1, A_2,...., A_i\\}max{A1\u200b,A2\u200b,....,Ai\u200b}\n\nYou are given this array BBB and asked to find any valid array AAA.\n\n**Note**: For a given array BBB solution always exists.\n\n\nInput Format\n\nThe first line of input will contain a single integer TTT, denoting the number of test cases.\nEach test case consists of multiple lines of input.\n\nThe first line of each test case contains an integer NNN.\nThe second line of each test case contains NNN space-separated integers B1,B2,\u2026,BNB_1, B_2, \\ldots, B_NB1\u200b,B2\u200b,\u2026,BN\u200b \u2014 the elements of array BBB.\n\n\n\n\nOutput Format\nFor each test case, output on a new line NNN space-separated integers A1,A2,\u2026,ANA_1, A_2, \\ldots, A_NA1\u200b,A2\u200b,\u2026,AN\u200b \u2014 the elements of array AAA.",
    "constraints": [
      "1\u2264T\u226410001 \\leq T \\leq 10001\u2264T\u22641000",
      "1\u2264N\u22641061 \\leq N \\leq 10^{6}1\u2264N\u2264106",
      "\u22122\u22c5106\u2264Ai\u22642\u22c5106-2 \\cdot 10^{6} \\leq A_{i} \\leq 2 \\cdot 10^{6}\u22122\u22c5106\u2264Ai\u200b\u22642\u22c5106",
      "\u2212106\u2264Bi\u2264106-10^{6} \\leq B_{i} \\leq 10^{6}\u2212106\u2264Bi\u200b\u2264106",
      "The sum of NNN over all test cases won't exceed 10610^6106."
    ],
    "inputFormat": "",
    "outputFormat": "",
