        "explanation": "Explanation:\nFor testcase 1:\nLet AAA = [3,\u22122,4][3, -2, 4][3,\u22122,4]\nB1B_1B1\u200b = A1A_1A1\u200b - A1A_1A1\u200b = 000\nB2B_2B2\u200b = A1A_1A1\u200b + A2A_2A2\u200b - max\\text{max}max(A1A_1A1\u200b, A2A_2A2\u200b) = 111 - 333 = -222\nB3B_3B3\u200b = A1A_1A1\u200b + A2A_2A2\u200b + A3A_3A3\u200b - max\\text{max}max(A1A_1A1\u200b, A2A_2A2\u200b, A3A_3A3\u200b) = 555 - 444 = 111"
      }
